  title:'Amsterdam Dance Event 2026',slug:'amsterdam-dance-event-2026-festmore',category:'festival',
  city:'Amsterdam',country:'NL',start_date:'2026-10-14',end_date:'2026-10-18',
  date_display:'14–18 October 2026',
  description:`Amsterdam Dance Event (ADE) is the world's leading electronic music conference and festival — a five-day extravaganza that transforms Amsterdam into the global capital of dance music each October. Over 400 events across 200 venues and 400,000 visitors make ADE the most concentrated electronic music experience on the planet.\n\nBy day, ADE operates as the most important industry conference in electronic music — with 600+ speakers, panel discussions, masterclasses, workshops and business sessions attended by DJs, producers, labels, promoters, agents and music technology companies from 120 countries. By night, Amsterdam's clubs, concert halls, warehouses, boats and outdoor spaces host an extraordinary programme of performances from the world's finest DJs and live electronic acts.\n\nADE's influence on global electronic music cannot be overstated — career-defining announcements, important industry deals and cultural conversations that shape the future of dance music happen at ADE every year. The combination of daytime industry programme and nighttime performances creates a week of unparalleled intensity and quality.\n\nFor food vendors, beverage brands and lifestyle retailers, ADE's 400,000 visitors — predominantly young, creative, international and high-spending — represent one of the finest trading opportunities in Amsterdam's busy autumn events calendar. The food offering around ADE venues is a key part of the festival experience.`,
