  title:'Rollende Keukens Amsterdam 2026',slug:'rollende-keukens-amsterdam-2026',category:'market',
  city:'Amsterdam',country:'NL',start_date:'2026-05-13',end_date:'2026-05-17',
  date_display:'13–17 May 2026',
  description:`Rollende Keukens (Rolling Kitchens) is Amsterdam's flagship street food festival — five days of extraordinary culinary diversity in the beautiful Westerpark, where over 200 food trucks, mobile kitchens and street food vendors from the Netherlands and across Europe present their finest cuisine to 250,000 hungry visitors.\n\nNow in its 19th year, Rollende Keukens has established itself as the premier street food event in the Netherlands and one of the most important in Europe. The festival's curated selection process ensures genuine quality and diversity — every cuisine from Dutch stroopwafels and Indonesian rijsttafel to Japanese ramen and Argentinian empanadas is represented by passionate food entrepreneurs.\n\nThe Westerpark setting — a former gas factory converted into one of Amsterdam's finest cultural parks — provides a perfect backdrop of industrial heritage and green space. Live music, craft beer, natural wine and artisan soft drinks complement the food offering throughout the five days and evenings.\n\nFor food truck owners and mobile catering businesses, Rollende Keukens is the most prestigious street food event in the Netherlands. Being selected is a mark of quality recognised throughout the Dutch food industry, and the event attracts buyers, food media and restaurant industry figures alongside the 250,000 members of the public.`,
