  city:'Amsterdam',country:'NL',start_date:'2026-06-04',end_date:'2026-06-07',
  date_display:'4–7 June 2026',
  description:`Taste of Amsterdam is the Dutch capital's premier food festival — four days of culinary excellence in the Amstelpark, where Amsterdam's finest restaurants, food entrepreneurs and artisan producers present their best to 50,000 food-passionate visitors.\n\nThe festival format gives visitors the opportunity to sample dishes from 20+ of Amsterdam's top restaurants alongside street food vendors, artisan producers and food innovators in a beautiful outdoor setting. Cooking demonstrations, masterclasses with Michelin-starred chefs and wine and beer pairings add depth to the experience beyond pure eating.\n\nAmsterdam's food scene has transformed dramatically over the past decade — the city now boasts 18 Michelin stars and is widely recognised as one of Europe's most exciting food destinations. Taste of Amsterdam showcases this transformation, presenting the breadth of the city's culinary ambition to a dedicated food-lover audience.\n\nFor food vendors and artisan producers, Taste of Amsterdam is the most prestigious food event in the Netherlands — a platform for quality and innovation that attracts food media, restaurant buyers and dedicated food enthusiasts alongside the 50,000 general visitors. Participation signals quality and positions a food business at the centre of Amsterdam's dynamic food scene.`,
